Target table: Application (logical: pei_application)
New column: pei_owningbu lookup → Business Unit

Block 1 — Add the column
Power Apps → EMS environment → Tables → Application → Columns tab → + New column.
Fill in:
Display name:
Owning BU
Description:
The Business Unit that owns this Application. Populated by Flow 1 (L1-A07) via the BU Org Unit Mapping table (L1-A02). Drives BU scoping for Risk Manager visibility, security role enforcement, and downstream rule evaluation.
Data type: Lookup
Related table: Business Unit
Required: Business Recommended
Searchable: ☑ (leave checked)
Click Advanced options.
Schema name (override the auto-suggested OwningBU):
owningbu
